About Karansul
#show Hero 1
#show Trapper 2
#ANIMATION 61
#CAMERA 3
#phrase Trapper  1
Karansul has me by the throat with both hands. All the locals hate him. Everyone is in debt to him, he buys our trophies for a trifle then sells them for three times more. But woe betide he who tries to find another buyer! Karansul is in league with the local rough element. One wrong move and he sends his cutthroat friends to deal with you. And that, my friend, is a goodbye of a permanent nature.
#ANIMATION 15
#CAMERA 2
#phrase Hero  2
Yes, I can see it is serious. But can you not think of a way to put some pressure on this vermin?
#ANIMATION 11
#CAMERA 11
#phrase Trapper  3
Let us make an honest agreement - you help me and I will help you. And if you do something for me, I will tell you all I know about the merchant. All right?
