What do you want me to do?
#ANIMATION 62
#CAMERA 11
#phrase Trapper  5
Quite simple... soon a fur buyer from the capital will come to this area. He offers good prices for skins, nothing like our mean pirate here. But I cannot get to the meeting place where he collects the skins, because Karansul's... ruffians will have their eyes on me.
